{
  "_comment": "MCP Inspector config — every server in stdio mode. Run from the repo root: `npx @modelcontextprotocol/inspector --config configs/inspector/all-stdio.json`. Pending servers point at their unmigrated entrypoints and will not initialize as real MCP until they are converted (see docs/migration/mcp-migration-tracker.md).",
